title: GTA Online: Money Fronts
headline: GTA Online: Money Fronts
subtitle: Higgins Helitours
content:
Once you’ve commandeered the Hands On Car Wash, take your money laundering operation to new heights by acquiring Higgins Helitours.

In addition to ferrying tourists through the sky, you’ll also get a cash boost for Air Freight Cargo along with the ability to request your own personal Higgins Maverick, plus personal and Pegasus helicopters be delivered to the helipad.

Purchase Higgins Helitours from Maze Bank Foreclosures or the For Sale sign outside the building.
